jy\xc4\x81 y\xc4\x81nti mady\xc4\x81jinopi m\xc4\x81m 9.25  \n  \npatra\xe1\xb9\x83 pu\xe1\xb9\xa3pa\xe1\xb9\x83 phala\xe1\xb9\x83 toya\xe1\xb9\x83 yo me bhakty\xc4\x81  \nprayacchati  \ntad aha\xe1\xb9\x83 bhaktyupah\xe1\xb9\x9btam a\xc5\x9bn\xc4\x81mi prayat\xc4\x81tmana\xe1\xb8\xa5  \n9.26  \n  \nyat karo\xe1\xb9\xa3i yad a\xc5\x9bn\xc4\x81si yaj juho\xe1\xb9\xa3i dad\xc4\x81si yat  \nyat tapasyasi kaunteya tat kuru\xe1\xb9\xa3va madarpa\xe1\xb9\x87am 9.27  \n  \n\xc5\x9bubh\xc4\x81\xc5\x9bubhaphalair eva\xe1\xb9\x83 mok\xe1\xb9\xa3yase karmabandhanai\xe1\xb8\xa5  \nsa\xe1\xb9\x83ny\xc4\x81sayogayukt\xc4\x81tm\xc4\x81 vimukto m\xc4\x81m upai\xe1\xb9\xa3yasi 9.28  \n  \nsamoha\xe1\xb9\x83 sarvabh\xc5\xabte\xe1\xb9\xa3u na me dve\xe1\xb9\xa3yosti na priya\xe1\xb8\xa5  \nye bhajanti tu m\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 bhakty\xc4\x81 mayi te te\xe1\xb9\xa3u c\xc4\x81py aham  \n9.29  \n  \napi cet sudur\xc4\x81c\xc4\x81ro bhajate m\xc4\x81m ananyabh\xc4\x81k  \ns\xc4\x81dhur eva sa mantavya\xe1\xb8\xa5 samyag vyavasito hi sa\xe1\xb8\xa5  \n9.30  \n  \nk\xe1\xb9\xa3ipra\xe1\xb9\x83 bhavati dharm\xc4\x81tm\xc4\x81 \xc5\x9ba\xc5\x9bvacch\xc4\x81nti\xe1\xb9\x83  \nnigacchhati  \nkaunteya pratij\xc4\x81n\xc4\xabhi na me bhakta\xe1\xb8\xa5 pra\xe1\xb9\x87a\xc5\x9byati 9.31  \n  \nm\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 hi p\xc4\x81rtha vyap\xc4\x81\xc5\x9britya yepi syu\xe1\xb8\xa5 p\xc4\x81payonaya\xe1\xb8\xa5  \nstriyo vai\xc5\x9by\xc4\x81s tath\xc4\x81 \xc5\x9b\xc5\xabdr\xc4\x81s tepi y\xc4\x81nti par\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 gatim  \n9.32  \n  \nki\xe1\xb9\x83 punar br\xc4\x81hma\xe1\xb9\x87\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5 pu\xe1\xb9\x87y\xc4\x81 bhakt\xc4\x81 r\xc4\x81jar\xe1\xb9\xa3ayas tath\xc4\x81  \nanityam asukha\xe1\xb9\x83 lokam ima\xe1\xb9\x83 pr\xc4\x81pya bhajasva m\xc4\x81m  \n9.33  \n  \nmanman\xc4\x81 bhava madbhakto mady\xc4\x81j\xc4\xab m\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 namaskuru  \nm\xc4\x81m evai\xe1\xb9\xa3yasi yuktvaivam \xc4\x81tm\xc4\x81na\xe1\xb9\x83 matpar\xc4\x81ya\xe1\xb9\x87a\xe1\xb8\xa5  \n9.34  \n 